{"tid":1385754,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"不忿石Sir被趕 《經濟》整治編採部 避寫「藤條」變「竹枝」","createTime":"2019-07-30T07:05:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T07:55:05.000Z","uid":108282,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"634b09ef91334efd0d82dd8ee66be32b9fc9e890","tid":1385754,"uid":108282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:05:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nkrRKC2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnkrRKC2.png&h=2851ef89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港經濟日報集團（423）前執行董事兼副社長石鏡泉，早前在撐警集會上發表藤條教仔的暴力言論，被社會譴責，又被數百位集團員工聯署批評，最後在股東David Webb逼宮之前辭職。<br />\n<br />\n據悉集團曾在內部電郵向員工保證，聯署的員工不會被秋後算帳，但有經濟日報編採部的員工近日向本報指，高層近星期密密召見各組同事，由於集團因政治事件出事，日後所有涉及政治的內容都要嚴加過濾，例如不可過份歌頌或讚揚示威者，又要持平刊登政府和國家立場，甚至明言若報道涉及「藤條」字眼都要避開，以免觸動讀者神經，再次遷怒石鏡泉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190730/59877795\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190730%2F59877795&d=BNsYvnDu2JTLJ%2Bl7stKmI1DHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=573ff620\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190730%2F59877795&h=c4cd0d40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190730/59877795</a>"},{"pid":"6871404bdd20eb80dcf325f935e7bd8047469121","tid":1385754,"uid":108282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:14:11.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"a74ff313ff5feac3a6c748d4dc50cf1c8ac44bee","tid":1385754,"uid":57297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:24:07.000Z","msg":"推到條仆街坐監先啦<br />\n<br />\n8月5號大罷工"},{"pid":"c490f2007ec8f26b3533676ed6b2c035596c9418","tid":1385754,"uid":108282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:52:54.000Z","msg":"逍遙法外"},{"pid":"298cc5763cb19ecb57b430bb8b176a9f8feed3f9","tid":1385754,"uid":1